title: Did Members of the NYPD Wear ‘I Can Breathe’ Shirts in 2020 Protest?
subtitle: A photograph showing men in "I Can Breathe" shirts, holding signs supporting the New York Police Department, went viral after the death of George Floyd.
author: Nur Ibrahim
vclaim: A photograph shows members of the NYPD wearing "I Can Breathe" shirts mocking the death of George Floyd.
